name: Yeet The Yeti
description: YEET is the coolest meme coin to hit the AVAX blockchain, designed to bring the community together for big gains, great vibes, and a snowstorm of fun. It’s more than just a token; it’s a movement for those who thrive on humor, energy, and the power of collective momentum. In the world of YEET, we don’t just move—we send it full force. The Yeti isn’t here to tiptoe through crypto—it’s here to charge forward, carving a unique space in the AVAX ecosystem where the community leads the way. If you’re ready for bold moves and bigger laughs, YEET is your ride.
